  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      goal of this study is to check the effecivity, feasibility and toxicity of the
      chemoradiotherapy and hyperthermia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Radiation: 5x1,8Gy until 50,4 Gy Hyperthermia: 2x/week

      Chemotherapy:

      neoadjuvant= day 1-5 and day 29-33 5FU 1000mg/m2 adjuvant = 4 Cycles 5FU 500mg/m2 all 4 weeks
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
